          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Incident Volume Report -- [Month]\n\nVolume (vs prior month):\n  SEV-1: 3 (-25%)  SEV-2: 8 (+0%)  SEV-3: 22 (-10%)  Total: 33 (-11%)\n\nNormalised rate: 2.1 incidents/million requests (vs 2.4 last month) -- IMPROVING\n\nTop root cause categories (90d rolling):\n  1. model-quality: 34%  (unchanged)\n  2. capacity: 25%       (up from 18% -- GPU provisioning gap)\n  3. integration: 20%    (down from 28% -- rate-limit fixes deployed)\n\nRecurrence rate: 18%  (target: < 10%) -- AT RISK\n\nActive systemic fix initiatives: 2\n  - token-budget-exhaustion (SEV-2, capacity) | due: [date] | ON TRACK\n  - embedding-drift-detection (SEV-2, model-quality) | due: [date] | AT RISK"
